data.title: Our Food
data.meta_description: Indulge in the irresistible delights of Pizza 73 - Our food is a symphony of taste, carefully curated to delight your senses. Explore the unparalleled taste of Pizza 73 today!
data.text:
The number 73 continues to deliver the tastiest, most crave-able pizza in Alberta. We cook up 21 varieties of specialty pizzas and offer 21 different toppings. We have 3 styles of regular crusts (Signature Pan, Sesame Seed, and Thin Crust), and 3 types of healthy alternative crusts (Gluten Free, Keto, and Cauliflower), no matter who you are and what you’re craving we've got you covered.

Top those crusts with one of our 7 types of mouth-watering sauces (Traditional, BBQ, Donair, Pesto, Buffalo, and Creamy Garlic) and you have thousands of different combinations to tickle your taste buds. 7 types of sauces, 3 types of crusts, and 21+ different toppings = 73 reasons to believe. If you’re craving a little something extra with your pizza, try some of our famous regular or boneless wings, the Golden Crispy wings are a fan favorite. Still not what your craving? Try our Cheesy Wedgies, Jalapeno Poppers, Deep Fried Shrimp, or Popcorn Chicken. Top those off with one of our amazing dips and now you've really got a party. The mystery and magic of the number 73 can be found all through our menu, just hiding below the surface.
